'''NBU''' can refer to * [[National Bee Unit]] - A leading bee research institute in the UK. * [[North Bengal University]] - A university in West Bengal, India. * [[National Bank of Ukraine]] - the central bank of Ukraine * [[NetBackup]] - an enterprise level backup and recovery suite. * [[New Bulgarian University]] - a private institution of higher education. * [[National Bank of Uzbekistan]] - an alternative name for the National Bank for Foreign Economic Activity of the Republic of Uzbekistan. * [[.nbu]] (Nokia Backup) - a file extension for Nokia mobile phone software. {{disamb}}
